              <p class="back-role">AI System Designer</p>
              <span class="back-meta">Mexico</span>
              <div class="back-divider"></div>
              <p class="back-desc" style="margin-top: auto;">AI-assisted production pipelines, brand systems, and content workflows. Local LLM deployments and automation tooling for creative teams.</p>
            </div>
